                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9292" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1392</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1241 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大牧人库存管理遇难题，数智化协同创新机</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Road to Inventory Management of Big Herdsman</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">范英杰，曲润贝，张嘉乐，国文豪，刘晓宁，张梦如，王晓，亓浩</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛大牧人机械股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">仓储部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">库存管理；数智化转型；价值链管理；降本增效；大牧人公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Inventory management, Digital-intelligence transformation, Value chain, Cost reduction and efficiency, Big Herdsman</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大牧人公司作为畜禽养殖设备领域的领军企业，注重技术创新和个性化定制，但随其发展速度加快，传统的库存管理方式已无法适应公司业务。库存管理成本上升且效率低下，无法满足企业定制化需求加大的发展状况。大牧人决定进行库存管理数智化转型，通过引入SRM、WMS、TMS等系统，实现采购、仓储、运输环节的数智化转型。在完成系统搭建后，大牧人公司据企业的扩张和提升效率的需求，借助企业高水平研发技术，在原有数智化基础上利用价值链协同库存管理，实现了与供应商和客户的信息共享和互通，帮助企业降本增效。通过不断数智化创新和持续改善，大牧人公司跻身行业领先的设备供应商行列。本案例旨在增强学生对库存管理重要性的认识，深入领悟数智化转型对企业库存管理的重要意义，掌握数智化库存管理的工具，引导学生从价值链协同角度理解企业数智化转型的重要性，并通过案例的学习提升学生思维拓展能力和分析能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Big Herdsman, a livestock breeding equipment leader, prioritized tech innovation and personalization. But its traditional inventory management fell behind business growth, causing rising costs and inefficiency. To address this, Big Herdsman digitized procurement, warehousing, and transportation via SRM, WMS, TMS systems. While this addressed information gaps, efficiency still lagged. Leveraging its R&amp;D, Big Herdsman enhanced the digitalized value chain, integrating suppliers and customers. This reduced costs, boosted efficiency, and positioned the company as an industry-leading supplier.This case aims to enhance students&#39; awareness of the importance of inventory management, to understand the significance of digital transformation for enterprise inventory management and the application of digital inventory management tools, to guide students to understand the importance of enterprise digital transformation from the perspective of value chain synergy, and to enhance students&#39; ability to diverge and analyze through the study of the case.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">库存管理；数智化转型；价值链管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-02</td>
                            </tr>
